data.description: Back on the market! Buyer's financing fell through. PRICED TO SELL!!! SELLER OFFERING $3,000 TOWARDS BUYERS CLOSING COST. This modern and contemporary flat offers exquisite views of Nashville's skyline. Gorgeous granite countertops, sleek white cabinetry, refined light flooring, stainless steel appliances, pantry, W/D connections, large closet space. Conveniently located on the community to the pool with outdoor kitchen and grill, dog park, clubhouse/lounge, fitness center, fire pit. Only five minutes from downtown Nashville and major corridors. Schedule your appointment today and make this your home!!
